data.description: $5,000 SELLER CONCESSION + Silver 14 MONTH BLUE RIBBON HOME WARRANTY offered to a Buyer at closing! Retreat to your own private oasis in this lovely 3 bed 2 bath featuring a private heated in-ground pool (fenced), covered gazebo with outlets, privacy fenced yard, stamped concrete patio, beautiful mature landscape, RV parking, finished 2 car garage AND more- all on a .45 acre lot! The ranch style home offers main level amenities and room for a crowd in the spacious dining and living space- both inviting you to stay with a cozy brick surround fireplace. A new roof, Anderson windows, 50 gallon water heater, central air, radiant heat, storage galore, mature landscape and sprinkler system top off some of the reasons not to miss this property. Assumable VA mortgage!
